    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1 H3C LA2608 室内无线网关用户手册"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                61,
                611,
                84
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.1 概述"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                102,
                196,
                122
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "H3C LA2608-GM/GU 室内无线网关（以下简称 LA2608）可以为用户提供无线服务，为了实现对设备的管理，LA2608 需要通过 3G/4G 网络连接到运营商无线控制器。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                138,
                907,
                174
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/07645668bfab67e81bac47a7c5f603401426be1b3216242f586546808fc27dab.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                146,
                188,
                184,
                212
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                188,
                198,
                223,
                212
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "目前，LA2608 只支持与 H3C 公司的无线控制器互通。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                224,
                561,
                239
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2 配置LA2608与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                282,
                484,
                302
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如 图 1 所示，LA2608 安装了SIM卡，通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器，并向用户提供无线服务。关于LA2608的安装方法，请参见“H3C LA2608室内无线网关 快速安装指南”。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                320,
                907,
                355
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/25307ddba26964ba7daa9dc6a1251a551313cc2a981ab84e8f9c0a0814a016fa.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "图1 配置 LA2608 与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                147,
                390,
                811,
                584
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2.1 配置LA2608"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                625,
                260,
                642
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(1) 配置拨号访问组的拨号控制列表"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                659,
                438,
                675
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "<LA2608>system-view "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                682,
                310,
                695
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]dialer-rule 1 ip permit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                146,
                699,
                413,
                713
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(2) 配置 DCC 拨号"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                716,
                305,
                732
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/39057cd15c7479a2fd918c53f2da062a7b3267cb4e170eaca2cd78b335a1f787.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                146,
                748,
                184,
                770
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                188,
                756,
                225,
                771
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "dialer number命令用来配置发起呼叫的拨号串，不同运营商的拨号串不同，请用户在配置前向网络运营商获取发起呼叫的拨号串。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                781,
                907,
                815
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]interface Cellular-Ethernet2/0  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]ip address cellular-allocated  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer enable-circular  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer-group 1  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer idle 0 "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "powershell"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                850,
                645,
                929
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_number",
            "content": {
                "page_number_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1 "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                505,
                948,
                515,
                958
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer autodial 5  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer number *99# autodial  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]nat outbound  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]quit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "powershell"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                51,
                626,
                115
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(3) 配置 DNS 解析功能"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                118,
                342,
                133
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]dns resolve "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                141,
                310,
                153
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(4) 配置静态路由"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                157,
                295,
                173
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]ip route-static 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 Cellular-Ethernet2/0 "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                181,
                660,
                194
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(5) 指定运营商无线控制器的 IP 地址"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                198,
                443,
                213
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608] wlan ac ip 60.191.99.143 "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                220,
                428,
                233
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2.2 配置运营商无线控制器"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                248,
                352,
                264
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/8ca3c3627f4ec48e0ec841e036f5ba63e3476d2417c3e8a168e49f82496c18a8.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                290,
                184,
                313
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                188,
                298,
                226,
                313
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如下配置仅供参考，运营商可根据实际情况进行调整。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                324,
                559,
                339
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(1) 创建业务 VLAN"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                374,
                312,
                389
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "<AC>system-view  \n[AC]vlan 2  \n[AC-vlan2] quit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "objectivec"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                397,
                275,
                442
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(2) 创建 WLAN-ESS 接口并加入业务 VLAN"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                447,
                500,
                461
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[AC]interfaceWLAN-ESS1   \n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]portaccessvlan2   \n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]quit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "objectivec"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                471,
                421,
                516
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(3) 配置明文方式的服务模板"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                521,
                383,
                536
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[AC]wlan service-template 1 clear  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]ssid ssidh3c  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]bind WLAN-ESS 1  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]service-template enable  \nPlease wait... Done.  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]quit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                543,
                463,
                638
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(4) 开启自动 AP 功能"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                644,
                327,
                659
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[AC]wlan auto-ap enable  \n[AC]wlan ap 2608 model LA2608 id 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]serial-id auto  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]radio 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]service-template 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]radio enable  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]quit  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]quit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "objectivec"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                667,
                515,
                796
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(5) 配置 VLAN 接口 IP 地址"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                800,
                374,
                815
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[AC]interface Vlan-interface 1   \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]ip address 60.191.99.143 255.255.0.0   \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]quit   \n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 2   \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]ip address 10.249.136.1 255.255.252.0   \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]quit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                824,
                635,
                920
            ]
        },
